{"tid":2131587,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"任志剛：勿低估美將金融武器化","createTime":"2020-07-30T03:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T10:29:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"9cabd992c5a99a3025b0a77b5dcde9121f38454f","tid":2131587,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:20:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/TK5W3D6UKFF3JPR4FZREQWVVOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FTK5W3D6UKFF3JPR4FZREQWVVOM%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhKwVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=4464a720\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FTK5W3D6UKFF3JPR4FZREQWVVOM%2F&h=325840be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/TK5W3D6UKFF3JPR4FZREQWVVOM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n任志剛：勿低估美將金融武器化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7MALVkj_1BRONEYJU5odowtsmzQ=/571x331/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FLFPDD23H3TJILS3S3MVL6H5L4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7MALVkj_1BRONEYJU5odowtsmzQ%3D%2F571x331%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFLFPDD23H3TJILS3S3MVL6H5L4.gif&h=e9a44ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任志剛昨出席團結香港基金論壇，稱金融體系仍然穩健。有線新聞畫面<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日前揚言擔心第三次金融危機正醞釀的行會成員兼金管局前總裁任志剛，昨出席團結香港基金論壇，再就當前中美對峙及制裁表達關注。美國務院90日內將列出清單，屆時可針對個人、官員、企業、金融機構甚至「核彈式」對準政府制裁，他擔心此舉或收緊香港參與使用美元交易，個人雖「唔希望會發生」，但籲市場「唔可以低估特朗普及蓬佩奧將金融武器化影響」。<br />\n<br />\n對港區國安法實施他亦。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指制裁對準政府屬「核彈級」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：聯合國：國安非限制人權理據<br />\n<br />\n據《香港自治法案》，與美。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n倘制裁對準特區政府及當局所持的美元國庫券全被凍結，則屬「核彈級武器」，甚至不排除因美債無法交收而出現違約，本港雖設有美元即時支付系統，由滙豐擔任美元清算行，但滙豐最後仍要回到紐約美聯儲就美元作終極清算。不過他估計美方官員會作理性決定，「唔相信制裁會去到針對政府層面」。<br />\n<br />\n卸任金管局舵手後，任早年曾發表學術文章，提出是時候檢討聯滙。被問及目前立場，他只笑說「自己也上了一課」，即使已退休，作為公職人員仍需謹言慎行，強調聯滙在港行之有效，絕對適宜繼續執行。"},{"pid":"d183059e899cb07c6abee33d66f1d9808d182ca3","tid":2131587,"uid":60120,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"自己也上了一課<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80a34cbb2ddeb744f21159ddd977091a179ec4a","tid":2131587,"uid":31215,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"基本法賦予<br />\n呢條友散播謠言製造恐慌<br />\n拉得"},{"pid":"6e1ea95a0e3fa777ea281316a2d2c7d9d7407469","tid":2131587,"uid":44171,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"早2日又講無影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eece4c470724a9ea2cb658c3744385d5130c9fe2","tid":2131587,"uid":224533,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"信基本法 信腐乳焗腸 唔怕"},{"pid":"dcd208ef5e8c2b6d7a91013742c98ab4e2d81b8f","tid":2131587,"uid":34779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"「唔相信制裁會去到針對政府層面」<br />\non9制裁唔針對政府咁針對邊個？"},{"pid":"3c5a26a1abaa059515d88c9ab4b1fb69ef0fc74f","tid":2131587,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:30:37.000Z","msg":"任總彈出彈入"},{"pid":"418169201d977cb1571acb09df5e994245ecf13f","tid":2131587,"uid":346701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4fLHC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4fLHC7.jpg&h=9c85f9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信黨"},{"pid":"c59569f26fa90f28865b08f042a90485a20826e2","tid":2131587,"uid":6058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"淆呀？<br />\n唔係好撚威做行會成員㗎咩？"},{"pid":"0ad99b5af43b9df8a787a21b2800dc5